# recall.word — the RECALL verb, a see of the past. Descends from word.word, see.word, chain.word,
# fold.word, can.word. Where see reads the present fold, recall reads the past, the facts on the
# chains, and folds them into a view, the story (seed/present/book/, the recall view-switcher).
# A view is a granted word. Which views a being recalls is a can, its consciousness levels.

A recall is a see of the past.
A see reads the present, a fold. A recall reads the past, the facts on the chains.
A recall folds the past into a view, the story of what was.
A view is a being's to recall when it can, its consciousness level.
